These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, accountant
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, soul
1. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | accountant | writer |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | disco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | mouse   | hedgehog      |
| Transport   | jet-ski | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, reggae
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, motorbike
1. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | punk    |
| Transport     | trike | motorbike |

